OL,3,CWhy councils in Wales are increasing
OL,4,Ctax and cutting services
OL,6,FIn a bid to keep up with growing
OL,7,Fdemand to care for an ageing
OL,8,Fpopulation and a rising number of
OL,9,Fchildren with Additional Learning
OL,10,FNeeds (ALNs), council tax has risen
OL,11,Fand other services have had to be cut.
OL,13,FSo how have councils crunched the
OL,14,Fnumbers and what difference will
OL,15,Fresidents see?
OL,17,FFor Jon Greatrex and his team, the
OL,18,Fcouncil's decision not to apply for
OL,19,FGreen Flag status has been tough but
OL,20,Fhe is now seeing it as a chance for
OL,21,Fchange.
