OL,3,CWhy councils in Wales are increasing
OL,4,Ctax and cutting services
OL,6,F"I think for wildlife and ecology
OL,7,Fmaybe it's going to be a different
OL,8,Fthing and i'm trying to get my head
OL,9,Faround, maybe we go down more of a
OL,10,Fcountry park model."
OL,12,FIt would mean more wilder areas, more
OL,13,Fwild flowers, more trees and less
OL,14,Fgrass cutting, "so we can do it more
OL,15,Fecologically," he added.
OL,17,FSwapping out expensive flowers is one
OL,18,Fway the council has given schools -
OL,19,Fwhich account for a huge chunk of its
OL,20,Fbudget - a 5% increase.
