OL,3,CWhy councils in Wales are increasing
OL,4,Ctax and cutting services
OL,6,FCadoxton Primary School in Barry
OL,7,Foffers a breakfast club to ensure
OL,8,Fchildren have a sit-down meal before
OL,9,Ftheir day's learning starts.
OL,11,FHeadteacher Janet Hayward said: "There
OL,12,Fis a portion of money that comes into
OL,13,Four school budget to pay for breakfast
OL,14,Fclub. The reality of that is it
OL,15,Fdoesn't come anywhere near paying for
OL,16,Fthe number of staff we need to
OL,17,Feffectively staff breakfast.
