OL,6,F"We have about 90 children at
OL,7,Fbreakfast every morning and it
OL,8,Fcertainly doesn't cover the money we
OL,9,Fneed for food."
OL,11,FMrs Hayward added that the budget
OL,12,Fincrease is a "drop in an ocean that
OL,13,Fdoesn't come anywhere close to
OL,14,Fproviding us with the funds that we
OL,15,Fneed to educate our children."
