OL,3,CWhy councils in Wales are increasing
OL,4,Ctax and cutting services
OL,6,FBudget shortfalls mean councils have
OL,7,Fto come up with news ways of making
OL,8,Fsavings. In the Vale of Glamorgan,
OL,9,Fresidents sort their own recycling. It
OL,10,Fmeans cartons, cans and packets can be
OL,11,Fsold - saving between #1.2-#1.4
OL,12,Fmillion a year.
OL,14,FLeader of the council, Lis Burnett,
OL,15,Fsaid the decisions her and her
OL,16,Fcolleagues have made over this year's
OL,17,Fbudget have been "absolutely
OL,18,Fimpossible."
