OL,6,FThe Labour Council Leader says she
OL,7,Fstill feels privileged to be in her
OL,8,Fposition but "sad" to not be able to
OL,9,Fdo more for residents.
OL,11,FShe said: "They're not difficult
OL,12,Fdecisions, they are absolutely
OL,13,Fimpossible decisions, because you know
OL,14,Fthat the decisions you are making are
OL,15,Factually going to affect people's
OL,16,Flives.
