OL,3,CWhy councils in Wales are increasing
OL,4,Ctax and cutting services
OL,6,F"Not one council leader in Wales, of
OL,7,Fany political party, came into
OL,8,Fpolitics to make cuts. Everybody tends
OL,9,Fto come into politics because of
OL,10,Fthings you want to achieve and that
OL,11,Fhasn't been possible for any council
OL,12,Fleader in Wales, and probably the UK,
OL,13,Ffor the last 14 years."
